Scenario: Verify Credit Card Payment Functionality

Preconditions:
- User has an active account with available balances
- User has added a credit card to their account

Steps:
1. Navigate to the login page
2. Enter valid login credentials
3. Click on the "Login" button
4. Navigate to the payment page
5. Enter payment amount
6. Select "Credit Card" as payment method
7. Enter credit card details (card number, expiration date, CVV)
8. Click on the "Submit" button
9. Verify that the payment is successful
10. Verify that the total balance has been updated

Expected Results:
- User should be able to successfully make a payment using their credit card
- The total balance should be updated after the payment is made

Test data:
- Valid login credentials
- Valid credit card details (card number, expiration date, CVV)
- Payment amount (e.g. $450)
